@startuml
title Use Case: Testify in Court

actor "Officer" as O
actor "Prosecutor" as P

usecase "Testify in Court" as UC

O --> UC : provides testimony
P --> UC : questions witness

UC .> (Receive Subpoena) : include
UC .> (Review Case File) : include
UC .> (Meet with Prosecutor) : include
UC .> (Appear in Court) : include
UC .> (Give Testimony) : include
UC .> (Document Appearance) : include

note right of UC
  Officer provides sworn testimony
  in legal proceedings related to
  cases they investigated or
  incidents they responded to.
end note
@enduml
